### 测试逻辑外键功能

### 1. 创建数据库连接
POST http://localhost:3000/database/connections
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试数据库",
  "dbType": "mysql",
  "host": "localhost",
  "port": 3306,
  "username": "root",
  "password": "password",
  "databaseName": "test_db"
}

### 2. 获取所有连接
GET http://localhost:3000/database/connections

### 3. 创建表
POST http://localhost:3000/database/tables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": 1,
  "tableName": "users",
  "tableComment": "用户表"
}

### 4. 创建另一个表
POST http://localhost:3000/database/tables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": 1,
  "tableName": "orders",
  "tableComment": "订单表"
}

### 5. 创建列
POST http://localhost:3000/database/columns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableId": 1,
  "columnName": "id",
  "dataType": "int",
  "isPrimary": true,
  "columnComment": "用户ID"
}

### 6. 创建另一个列
POST http://localhost:3000/database/columns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableId": 1,
  "columnName": "name",
  "dataType": "varchar(100)",
  "isNullable": false,
  "columnComment": "用户姓名"
}

### 7. 创建订单表的列
POST http://localhost:3000/database/columns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableId": 2,
  "columnName": "id",
  "dataType": "int",
  "isPrimary": true,
  "columnComment": "订单ID"
}

### 8. 创建订单表的用户ID列
POST http://localhost:3000/database/columns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableId": 2,
  "columnName": "user_id",
  "dataType": "int",
  "isNullable": false,
  "columnComment": "用户ID"
}

### 9. 创建逻辑外键关系
POST http://localhost:3000/database/foreign-keys
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceTableId": 2,
  "sourceColumnName": "user_id",
  "targetTableId": 1,
  "targetColumnName": "id",
  "relationType": "many-to-one"
}

### 10. 获取连接及其关联的表
GET http://localhost:3000/database/connections/1/with-tables

### 11. 获取表及其关联的列和外键关系
GET http://localhost:3000/database/tables/1/with-relations

### 12. 获取表及其关联的列和外键关系
GET http://localhost:3000/database/tables/2/with-relations

### 13. 获取表的外键关系
GET http://localhost:3000/database/tables/1/foreign-keys

### 14. 获取表的外键关系
GET http://localhost:3000/database/tables/2/foreign-keys 